            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>v1.0.1 — first-launch + auto-update banner</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixes the <strong>+ button</strong> being disabled on first install (no brands → no entry point). You can now click + on a brandless install; the inline brand picker prompts you to create your first brand.</li>
                    <li>Adds an inline <strong>auto-update banner</strong> so future updates surface as "Install Now / Later" inside the app instead of Sparkle's default sheet.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
